La Tonnellerie Hotel

Small charming 3 star hotel, situated on the Loire valley, between Blois
and Orléans

The bedrooms of the hotel

   16 bedrooms of a different kind, offering today’s comfort but keeping
   the character of a historic private House

Classic bedrooms on the village side

   All different, with the same comfort than the other bedrooms of the
   house, they overlook the quiet street of “les eaux bleues”…

Classic bedrooms on the garden side

   The quitness and the birdsong will be your sound environment…

Junior suite on the garden side

   Spacious with a little sitting area within the room, they overlook the
   quiet garden…

Family bedrooms

   Two connecting bedrooms sharing a large bathroom…

The Tonnellerie World

   The long history of the House and the strong environmental approach
   chosen make of this establishment a unique place for a stay in the
   region of the Loire valley Castles.

The history of the property

   Two centuries in the heart of the village!

The environmental approach

   Give meaning to our presence on this site, to your stay here…

The restaurant

   A simple cuisine but made with top-quality products localy sourced if
   possible…

